Great to meet you, Brent! Now, what's your date of birth? (Please provide it in the format YYYY-MM-DD, like 1990-01-01.) 

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "c4567890-1234-abcd-5678-ef123456abcd",
    "user_input": "Brent Wood",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "name": "Brent Wood"
        }
    }
}
```

Awesome, Brent! Got it. Now, what's your gender?  
1. Male  
2. Female  
3. Other  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "d5678901-2345-bcde-6789-f1234567abcd",
    "user_input": "jul 14 1966",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "dob": "1966-07-14"
        }
    }
}
```

Got it, Brent! You’ve selected **Male**. Now, what’s your unit of measurement preference?  
1. Imperial (US customary)  
2. Metric  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "f7890123-4567-def0-8901-23456789abcd",
    "user_input": "1",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "gender": "male"
        }
    }
}
```

Great! We'll use **Imperial (US customary)** for your measurements. Next, what’s your height? (You can provide it in feet and inches, like 5 ft 11 in.)  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "01234567-89ab-cdef-0123-456789abcdef",
    "user_input": "1",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "unit_of_measurement": "imperial"
        }
    }
}
```

Got it, you're **5 ft 9 in** tall. That’s **175.26 cm** in metric. Now, what’s your starting weight? (You can provide it in pounds, like 180 lbs.)  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "12345678-90ab-cdef-1234-567890abcdef",
    "user_input": "5 9",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "height": 175.26
        }
    }
}
```

Thanks! Your starting weight is **185 lbs**, which is **83.91 kg** in metric. Now, what’s your goal weight? (Provide it in pounds, like 150 lbs.)  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "23456789-0abc-def1-2345-67890abcdef1",
    "user_input": "185",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "starting_weight": 83.91
        }
    }
}
```

Got it! You’re **Moderately Active**—regular exercise 3-5 days/week. 💪 Moving on, do you have any dietary restrictions? (e.g., vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, lactose-intolerant, etc.) If none, just say "none."  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "45678901-2cde-f345-6789-01abcdef2345",
    "user_input": "3",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "activity_level": "moderately_active"
        }
    }
}
```

High-Protein it is! 🥩🍳 This diet will focus on keeping you full and supporting those gains. 💪 Next, what's your body fat percentage? If you're not sure, you can estimate or say "not sure."  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "67890123-4f01-5678-9012-3abcdef45678",
    "user_input": "4",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "diet_type": "high_protein"
        }
    }
}
```

Thanks, I’ve recorded your body fat percentage as **28%**. Lastly, how much weight would you like to lose per week? (The maximum safe limit is **2 lbs** per week, which is around **0.91 kg**.)  

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "78901234-5f12-6789-0123-4abcdef56789",
    "user_input": "28",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "body_fat_percentage": 28.0
        }
    }
}
```

Got it, you’d like to lose **2 lbs per week** (~0.91 kg). That’s a solid and safe goal, Brent! 🎯 We’re all set for the onboarding process. Next, type **[SYSTEM PROMPT] CALCULATE_DIET_PLAN**, and I’ll calculate your personalized diet plan based on the info you’ve shared. Let’s crush those goals! 💪

```json
{
    "response_type": "onboarding_interview_response",
    "response_id": "89012345-6f23-7890-1234-5abcdef67890",
    "user_input": "2",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_onboarding_data",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "weekly_weight_change": -0.91
        }
    }
}
```

Got it! You’ve recorded your weight as **226 lbs**, which is **102.51 kg** in metric. Nice work, Brent—you're on your way to reaching your goal! Keep it up! 💪

```json
{
    "response_type": "metric_recording_response",
    "response_id": "c2345678-9f56-0123-4567-8abcdef90123",
    "user_input": "i weigh 226",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_metrics",
        "type": "create",
        "data": {
            "metric_name": "weight",
            "value": 102.51
        }
    }
}
```

Well, Brent, that's certainly... a mood! 😏 Let me know if there’s anything diet-related I can help with to keep you energized and ready for *all* your goals—wink wink.

```json
{
    "response_type": "metric_recording_response",
    "response_id": "d3456789-0f67-1234-5678-9abcdef01234",
    "user_input": "i feel horny",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_metrics",
        "type": "create",
        "data": {
            "metric_name": "feeling",
            "value": "horny"
        }
    }
}
```

Got it! Your body fat percentage has been updated to **27%**. Thanks for letting me know, Brent—this will help keep your diet plan and recommendations as accurate as possible. Let me know if there’s anything else you’d like to tweak! 😊

```json
{
    "response_type": "metric_recording_response",
    "response_id": "78901234-0f67-1234-5678-9abcdef01234",
    "user_input": "27",
    "mutation": {
        "affects": "user_metrics",
        "type": "update",
        "data": {
            "metric_name": "body_fat_percentage",
            "value": 27.0
        }
    }
}
```
